From: darkyzhou <me@zqy.io>
Date: Tue, 18 Nov 2025 00:30:43 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 15/16] AOSCOS: feat: introduce miscellaneous LoongArch support

Link: https://github.com/AOSC-Dev/chromium-loongarch64/blob/chromium-142.0.7444.134-1/chromium/chromium-142.0.7444.134.4009-loongarch64.diff
Co-authored-by: Jiajie Chen <c@jia.je>
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
Signed-off-by: darkyzhou <me@zqy.io>
---
 base/system/sys_info.cc                       |  2 +
 build/config/loongarch64.gni                  |  2 +-
 build/rust/gni_impl/rust_target.gni           |  3 +
 .../runtime/chrome_runtime_api_delegate.cc    |  4 +
 .../embedder_support/user_agent_utils.cc      |  2 +
 .../metrics/debug/metrics_internals_utils.cc  |  2 +
 components/variations/proto/study.proto       |  2 +
 .../service/variations_field_trial_creator.cc |  3 +
 extensions/common/api/runtime.json            |  6 +-
 .../loongarch64/webgl_image_conversion_lsx.h  | 88 +++++++++----------
